"""
Book Model Permissions:

- can_view: Allows viewing the list of books.
- can_create: Allows adding new books.
- can_edit: Allows editing existing books.
- can_delete: Allows deleting books.

Groups and usage:

- Admins: Full permissions (view, create, edit, delete)
- Editors: Partial permissions (view, create, edit)
- Viewers: Read-only (view)

Views are protected using @permission_required decorators
with raise_exception=True to enforce these permissions.
"""
